          <div class="text-white/80">Inventory Managed</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">98%</div>
          <div class="text-white/80">Customer Satisfaction</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%# Testimonials Section %>
  <section class="mb-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-[#0055A4] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">What Our Clients Say</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Testimonials</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Hear from Ghanaian businesses that have transformed their operations with SupplyFlow.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-16 h-16 bg-[#0055A4] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "SupplyFlow has helped me keep track of my inventory even when there's no internet. I used to lose track of stock during power outages, but now I can continue working and everything syncs when the connection returns. My business has grown 30% since I started using it."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#00A86B] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 text-white">
            <span class="font-bold text-lg">KM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Kofi Mensah</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Owner, Electronics Shop, Kumasi</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-16 h-16 bg-[#00A86B] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-4xl">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "The mobile money integration saves me hours every day. Before SupplyFlow, I had to manually record each payment, but now everything is tracked automatically. The reports helped me secure a loan to expand my business. The support team is always available on WhatsApp when I need help."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0055A4] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 text-white">
            <span class="font-bold text-lg">AD</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Ama Darko</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Owner, Fashion Boutique, Accra</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg relative hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-16 h-16 bg-[#FFD700] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[#0055A4] text-4xl">
          <i class="fas fa-quote-right"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 italic">
          "As a distributor with multiple locations, I needed a solution that could help me manage inventory across all my shops. SupplyFlow's multi-location feature has been a game-changer. I can now see stock levels at each location and transfer products between shops easily. The affordable pricing means I can give access to all my staff without breaking the bank."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#0055A4] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 text-white">
            <span class="font-bold text-lg">EO</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Emmanuel Osei</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Owner, Distribution Company, Takoradi</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%# CTA Section %>
  <section class="mb-12 text-center">
    <div class="bg-[#00A86B] text-white rounded-3xl py-16 px-8 relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Decorative elements -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 bg-pattern"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full opacity-10 blur-xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[#FFD700] rounded-full opacity-10 blur-xl"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Join hundreds of Ghanaian businesses that use SupplyFlow to manage their inventory and increase profits.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="#" class="bg-white text-[#00A86B] hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg text-lg">
            Start Free 14-Day Trial
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all duration-300 text-lg">
            Schedule a Demo
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-white/80 text-sm">
          No credit card required. Cancel anytime.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
